chips.note: Monza R6-A and Monza R6-B share the same tag model number. To distinguish the two tag chip varieties with the TID, the user must refer to the wafer mask revision value in Bits 30h-32h. Monza R6-A has a wafer mask revision value of 000b while Monza R6-B has a wafer mask revision value of 001b.
